    "updated_at": "2016-03-30T16:32:31Z",
    "body": "after doing even more research today, it appears that apparently bootstrap was actually at fault here. by body tag takes on a height of effectively 0 when the viewport is above medium, 768px. thus making it so that when the console was opened, the size dipped below 768 and showed the style. whereas any other time, the width was over 768 and the style wasn't shown.\n"
